Ma'am.

67
00:14:32.414 --> 00:14:33.498
Excuse me...

68
00:14:33.749 --> 00:14:35.125
Is this Natre's house?

69
00:14:37.127 --> 00:14:38.295
What do you want?

70
00:14:39.588 --> 00:14:40.589
Well...

71
00:14:41.006 --> 00:14:43.133
