72
00:14:44.134 --> 00:14:46.094
Natre's friends? Come inside.

73
00:14:57.189 --> 00:14:59.650
Have some water. You must be tired.

74
00:15:00.025 --> 00:15:01.610
Did you drive from Bangkok?

75
00:15:02.819 --> 00:15:03.820
Yes.

76
00:15:06.949 --> 00:15:10.953
