98
00:17:57.327 --> 00:18:01.248
And these shadows appeared

99
00:18:04.835 --> 00:18:06.044
I think that...

100
00:18:07.296 --> 00:18:10.382
Natre's spirit is restless.

101
00:18:11.842 --> 00:18:13.093
Natre...

102
00:18:16.722 --> 00:18:18.182
My dear Natre.

103
00:18:20.392 --> 00:18:22.311
Why don't you visit me?

104
00:18:30.777 --> 00:18:33.197
Can you tell me what happened?

105
00:18:34.072 --> 00:18:35.741
Why she left Bangkok?

106
00:18:44.249 --> 00:18:45.542
Ma'am...

107
00:18:47.753 --> 00:18:48.921
Ma'am.

108
00:18:50.297 --> 00:18:51.924
These shadows...

109
00:18:52.508 --> 00:18:55.844
