114
00:19:22.663 --> 00:19:24.414
She wouldn't talk to anyone.

115
00:19:24.998 --> 00:19:27.000
No one knows what happened in Bangkok.

116
00:19:28.961 --> 00:19:31.129
Then she overdosed on pills.

117
00:19:31.839 --> 00:19:34.258
Luckily. her mother found her...

118
00:19:34.633 --> 00:19:36.468
and got her to the hospital on time.

119
00:19:36.969 --> 00:19:39.263
When she recovered...

120
00:19:40.597 --> 00:19:43.433
