122
00:19:47.771 --> 00:19:50.566
Why wouldn't her mom cremate her?

123
00:19:52.651 --> 00:19:55.904
She's been distraught
ever since Natre's death.

124
00:19:56.655 --> 00:20:00.284
No matter what she refused to cremate her.

125
00:20:01.660 --> 00:20:03.829
All the villagers were scared.

126
00:20:04.204 --> 00:20:06.999
No one wanted to socialize with her.

127
00:22:09.746 --> 00:22:10.956
Can't sleep?

128
00:22:16.795 --> 00:22:18.839
Tell me the truth...

129
00:22:19.798 --> 00:22:21.466
Did you love Natre?

130
00:22:25.262 --> 00:22:27.014
I tried to...

131
00:22:33.270 --> 00:22:35.772
I believed that one day I would.

132
00:22:41.528 --> 00:22:43.447
But I was fooling myself.

133
00:22:51.455 --> 00:22:52.873
When I broke it off...

134
00:22:54.124 --> 00:22:56.543
I was a total asshole.

135
00:23:02.549 --> 00:23:04.468
But she still loved me the same.

136
00:23:11.058 --> 00:23:12.893
I want this to be over.

137
00:23:14.978 --> 00:23:17.397
If she wants me to die I will.

138
00:23:18.482 --> 00:23:20.150
Don't say that.

139
00:23:21.151 --> 00:23:22.736
It's almost over.

140
00:23:24.112 --> 00:23:25.239
No it's not.

141
00:23:30.410 --> 00:23:32.663
I know she'll come for me.

142
00:23:33.580 --> 00:23:34.623
Tun.

143
00:23:35.541 --> 00:23:37.209
We've come this far.

144
00:23:39.545 --> 00:23:41.505
And you're sorry for what you did.

145
00:23:42.506 --> 00:23:44.049
I'm sure she knows.

146
00:23:46.426 --> 00:23:48.053
Don't talk about death anymore.

147
00:23:55.185 --> 00:23:56.562
I'm sorry.

148
00:24:02.192 --> 00:24:03.986
