160
00:27:51.004 --> 00:27:52.881
How could you leave me?

161
00:29:32.189 --> 00:29:33.398
Tun...

162
00:29:33.774 --> 00:29:35.317
Are you feeling better?

163
00:29:37.861 --> 00:29:39.863
