164
00:29:41.365 --> 00:29:42.407
Tun...

165
00:29:44.076 --> 00:29:45.035
Jane...

166
00:29:45.244 --> 00:29:46.370
Jane...

167
00:29:53.544 --> 00:29:54.461
The abbot said...

168
00:29:54.670 --> 00:29:56.630
