177
00:32:16.436 --> 00:32:17.771
You went on vacation?

178
00:32:18.605 --> 00:32:19.648
To the beach.

179
00:32:20.190 --> 00:32:21.316
When did you go?

180
00:32:22.025 --> 00:32:23.569
Last week.

181
00:32:25.904 --> 00:32:27.906
This photo is...

182
00:32:31.410 --> 00:32:32.578
What's wrong?

183
00:32:38.750 --> 00:32:40.002
You look fatter.

184
00:32:42.379 --> 00:32:43.755
I didn't recognize you.

185
00:32:46.258 --> 00:32:47.217
Hi.

186
00:32:48.218 --> 00:32:49.428
Jumbo prints.

187
00:32:51.138 --> 00:32:52.389
Write you name. please.

188
00:35:31.840 --> 00:35:33.091
Get her guys!

189
00:36:08.752 --> 00:36:09.878
Jane...

190
00:36:10.254 --> 00:36:12.005
