218
00:39:31.580 --> 00:39:33.790
Till death do us part!

219
00:39:38.879 --> 00:39:40.506
She's gone now.

220
00:41:19.771 --> 00:41:21.023
Sometimes...

221
00:41:21.231 --> 00:41:23.567
